[
  {
    "id": "TALK_LUMBERMILL_FABRICATE",
    "//": "This is all the dialogue related to buying bulk wood. TO-DO - Use variables to refine shop system. See SCRIPT_EFFECTS.md and isolated road fabriation system.",
